com.ibm.watson.dsm.platform.tuples

Interface ITupleSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<ITuple>, ISharedData<ITupleSetDescriptor>, java.lang.Iterable<ITuple>, java.util.List<ITuple>, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TupleSet

    public interface ITupleSet
extends java.util.List<ITuple>, java.io.Serializable, ISharedData<ITupleSetDescriptor>
    A set of tuples. TODO: the excluded columsn are to support time stamps in tuples, which are generally ignored in comparisions. We should really have a special ITimeStampedTuple or something that hides this.
    Author:
    dawood
